OL,5,Cattacks
OL,7,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,8,Fafter a council estate in the Scottish
OL,9,FBorders sustained thousands of pounds
OL,10,Fin damages, and had 40 windows smashed
OL,11,Fin a "deliberate" series of incidents.
OL,13,FPolice were called to Sprouston Road
OL,14,Fin the Newtown St Boswells area at
OL,15,Faround 9pm on Wednesday 23 July.
OL,17,FIt comes after multiple other
OL,18,Fincidents of damage to the estate, and
OL,19,Fadjoining community wing, throughout
OL,20,FJuly.
