OL,7,FPolice Scotland have said that the
OL,8,Fdamage to the area comes at over
OL,9,F#5,000.
OL,11,FConstable John Murray, from the
OL,12,FSelkirk Community Policing Team, said:
OL,13,F"This damage is a deliberate and re-
OL,14,Foccurring act to the council estate
OL,15,Fand is amounting to a significant
OL,16,Famount of money.
