OL,7,F"I would urge anyone in the local
OL,8,Fcommunity who has noticed anyone
OL,9,Facting suspiciously in the area over
OL,10,Fthe past month to speak to police.
OL,11,FAdditionally, if you have any private
OL,12,FCCTV close to the area, please get in
OL,13,Ftouch."
OL,15,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,16,Fcontact Police Scotland on 101,
OL,17,Fquoting incident number 3476 of 23
OL,18,FJuly.
